explanations.reason: The paper focuses on examining factors influencing online shopping intention in Vietnam using the Theory of Planned Behavior (TPB) and Technology Acceptance Model (TAM). The methodologies used include scale reliability test, exploratory factor analysis (EFA), correlation analysis, and regression analysis. None of the provided keywords related to machine learning, deep learning, or other advanced computational techniques are mentioned or implied in the title or abstract. The study is grounded in behavioral theories and statistical analysis rather than computational or machine learning approaches.
